* Iron Raptor had shook Prowler�s hand before she managed to see Prowl come 
around a corner and walk towards her, wondering if he had learned his lesson 
about calling her names yet.
But, she still didn�t fail on seeing the jealous glint in his optics when he 
had seen her touch Hot Rod, also wondering if he would ever get it through 
his head that she had no interest in other men and wasn�t planning to leave 
him any time soon.
Iron Raptor greeted Prowl with a smile, since she had also been worried 
about him since the last battle and was relieved to see that he was 
alright.*

� Hello.�

* But she barely had any other time to say anything else before there was a 
report over the com-links, Firearm finally decided to get in gear with the 
rescue mission for Dinobot and Tavatron. Though, that also meant that Prowl 
would have to go now, when she actually wanted him around.
Iron Raptor sigh as she watched all three men run from the room and head 
towards the CF exits, ready to save the two Maximals that she had been so 
worried about.
And again, she was left alone. Looking at the door her lover had left by, to 
go on a more important mission. Left alone with her thoughts, and an empty 
feeling as well.
They were always too busy with something to be together anymore, Prowl and 
herself.And now he ran off to another battle, one that she had to face the 
fact that...he might not return from. And even the thought of it ciezed her 
spark, wishing lik never before that he would had tried to hug her...and she 
would have let him.
